abstract_ssm: This collection consists of photographs by Claire Yaffa of children with AIDS, taken over a ten-year period at the Incarnation Children's Hospital in the Bronx.  Also included are a series of 1991 photographs of the potter's field on Hart Island, where many of these children are buried.
